review_title: Great watch. Fits my running and biking needs well.
reviews: Good size and fit. Needs a software update after opening the box.ake sure to rince after each workout to prevent salt build up in the buttons, making them sticky
It's great, nice and light, but have to go half size up to fit wider feet.
Fits like a glove and the touching the phone screen is accurate.
Survived the cooking direct on a camp fire. Made delicious steak.
Concise and gives great examples of modern day IT issues. But sometimes can be shallow.
